<opener><lb/><choice><orig>AD</orig><reg>Ad</reg></choice> Dominum Michelottum.</opener>
<p><lb/>Dolui sane non parum postquam ex binis Tuis ultimis
  <lb/>quas ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> meum misisti <rs key="B_991170515019105501 B_991170515019205501" type="letter">epistolis</rs> intellexi, omnes
         <lb/>Tuos labores, quos hactenus impendisti ad negotium
       <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinum</rs> promovendum, cathedramque Mathema<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ticam in Illustri <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>o <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavino</rs></rs> vacuam
       <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> vel mihi procurandam, irritos fuisse. Rem
  <lb/>ego confectam credebam perlectis duabus Tuis <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517052905501 B_991170517053105501">episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lis</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> antehac eodem die acceptis et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te sub
       <lb/>idem fere tempus per diversas vias <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs>
<lb/>transmissis, quibus ipsi petitum honorarium 1500<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>
          <lb/>thalerorum uncialium <abbr>Illmor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr> et <abbr>Excellmor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr>
<lb/><abbr>Dnor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr> <abbr>Reformator<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr> nomine promittebas, majorem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que in modum rogabas, ut salarium hoc accipere
         <lb/>ne dedignaretur. Serio hoc <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te factum fuisse
          <lb/>et jussu pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dictor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <abbr>Dnor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr> Reformatorum, no<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bis persuaderat maxima quam adhibuisti di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ligentia, ut <add>alterutra</add> <rs key="B_991170517052905501 B_991170517053105501" type="letter">epistola<add>r<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add></rs> Tua<add>rum</add> quibus dictum pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>missum continebatur secure ad nos perveni<subst><del>an</del><add>a</add></subst>t
         <lb/>mittendo per duas diversas vias duas ejusdem
  <lb/>contenti <rs key="B_991170517052905501 B_991170517053105501" type="letter">epistolas</rs>. At aliter rem se habere
         <lb/>ex nuperrimis Tuis comperimus, quibus nun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tias <abbr>Illmos</abbr> et <abbr>Excllmos</abbr> <choice><abbr>Dos</abbr><expan>Dominos</expan></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670">Reformatores</rs> in
          <lb/>majorem su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am quam 1500<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> florenorum
         <lb/>vestratium non consensisse, nec unquam
         <lb/>consensuros esse. Quibus ita se habentibus
         <pb facs="1038316" n="2"/>
<lb/>irritum omnino est negotium nostrum, libe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rumque se credit <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> ab obligatione
          <lb/>qua se constrinxerat petendo salarium 1500<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>
         <lb/>thalerorum uncialium, et inquam <!-- prüfen ob hier inquam oder in quam--> aegre
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> paucis quibusdam amicis <add>adductus</add> consenserat. Ais
         <lb/>salarium 1500<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> florenor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Venetorum, quod
        <lb/><abbr>Illmi</abbr> et <abbr>Excllmi</abbr> <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Reformatores</rs> ipsi offe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>runt, insolitum esse maxime neminique
         <lb/>antehac oblatum, sed cogita qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, rem esse
         <lb/>adhuc magis insolitam, ut quis ea <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tate
  <lb/>quam <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> meus habet, relictis domi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-108991332X">uxo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re</rs> et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-1153514060 pers_DE-588-118656503 pers_DE-588-1089913494 pers_DE-588-117589136 pers_DE-588-1089913311">liberis</rs><note type="comment">Zu diesem Zeitpunkt hatten Johann I Bernoulli und Dorothea Falkner sechs Kinder, Nic. II B., Anna Katharina, Dan. I B., Dorothea, Joh. II B. und Jacob. Siehe <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_QBHJ796E">René Bernoulli-Sutter, 1792</rs>, p. 56.</note> compluribus maximam partem
         <lb/>in infantia constitutis, peregrinas in oras et
         <lb/>at divers<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> religionis homines discedat, post<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam melioribus conditionibus apud su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>religionis homines, in <rs key="place_VER-hollan" type="place">Hollandia</rs> nempe, una
  <lb/>cum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-108991332X">uxore</rs> ipsa et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-1153514060 pers_DE-588-118656503 pers_DE-588-1089913494 pers_DE-588-117589136 pers_DE-588-1089913311">liberis</rs> degere, ibique
  <lb/>educationi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-1153514060 pers_DE-588-118656503 pers_DE-588-1089913494 pers_DE-588-117589136 pers_DE-588-1089913311">liberorum</rs> suorum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>esse po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tuisset. His et aliis non minoris momenti obstaculis
       <lb/>impeditus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> m<unclear>al</unclear>uit omnino <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> petitione salarii abstine<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re, quam tale exigere quod par esset obstaculis istis
       <lb/>amoliendis, at quod ab <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr><abbr> D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person"><abbr>Refor.</abbr></rs> modeste expectare
         <lb/><add>non</add> posset. Verum cum instantius urgeres ut peteret salarium
          <lb/>quantumvis magnum aut scriberet se nullis plan<subst><del><gap/></del><add>e</add></subst> condi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionibus <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> <subst><del>a</del><add>e</add></subst>vocatum iri, et spem faceres pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1038317" n="3"/><lb break="no"/>laudatos <abbr>Dos</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Reformatores</rs> <add>qui</add> vocatione <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> <add>mei</add> Studii
       <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs> honori optime consultu<subst><del>ri essent</del><add>m vellent</add></subst>, in omnia
       <lb/>consensuros esse, annuit tandem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> petiitque sti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pendium non <subst><del>minoris</del><add>majoris</add></subst>  certe su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quam illa quam
       <lb/>apud <rs key="place_GEO-2996944" type="place">Lugdunenses</rs> ex salario annuo et <subst><del>collegiis</del><add>lectionibus</add></subst> privatis
  <lb/>habere potuisset; attamen ne ipse <rs type="organisation">cathedram</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nam</rs> ambiisse videretur subjunxit <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515019305501">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>,
    <lb/>ut si existimares has conditiones inutiliter <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Refor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matoribus</rs> propositum iri, supprimeres illam meique
         <lb/>ipsius vero co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationem unice porro urgeres,
       <lb/>qu<subst><del>am</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add></subst> <add>forte</add> optato successu carituram non fuisse<add>t</add>, <subst><del>spe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rat</del><add><lb/></add></subst> si nulla spes obtinendi <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr>
<lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Ref.</rs> injecta fuisset. Sed pluribus responderet
       <lb/><subst><del>ips</del><add>Ti</add></subst>bi ipse <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs>,<del> sed</del> nisi responsionem suam
  <lb/>aliquandiu adhuc impedirent negotia gravissima quibus nunc temporis obrutus est.<del>Interea si q<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
          <lb/>in mei utilitatem et favorem facere poteris, gra-
    <lb/>tum grati<subst><del>o</del><add>as</add></subst> agnosco ago maximas pro beneficiis
          <lb/>mihi exhibitis. Interea gratus agnosco</del> Interea
    <lb/><del>sique in mei utilitatem</del>devincies me <subst><del>t</del><add>T</add></subst>ibi ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>xime si qu<unclear><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></unclear> in mei utilitatem fore videbis, por<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro efficere non dignaberis. Fasciculus <rs key="biblio_WPXENY2H biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">librorum</rs>
          <lb/>quem <rs key="place_GEO-2657896" type="place">Tigurum</rs> misimus, dehinc ad Illustrissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum <abbr>Dnum</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924399" type="person">Capellum</rs> <choice><abbr>Ser.</abbr><expan>Serenissimae</expan></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven"><choice><abbr>Reipubl.</abbr><expan>Reipulicae</expan></choice></rs> nomine
         <pb facs="1038318" n="4"/>
<lb/>olim apud Tigurinos Residentem<note type="comment">Giacomo Cappello (ca. 1660/65-1736) war von 1707 bis 1711 venezianischer Resident in Zürich.</note> <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place"><del>Venetias</del></rs>
<lb/>transmittendum Tibique tradendum, nescio
  <lb/>quo fato <rs key="place_GEO-2657896" type="place">Tiguri</rs> mansit, eum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">amic<unclear>o</unclear></rs> qui bre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vi in vestras proficiscetur oras perferendum
       <lb/>tradam.<note type="comment">Es handelt sich vermutlich um dieselbe Büchersendung, von der Johannes Scheuchzer in seinem <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515085105501">Brief an Joh. I B. von 1714.09.09</rs>, und die nun nicht von Cappello sondern von Scheuchzer selbst, der nach Venedig reist, mitgenommen werden soll.</note></p><closer> <salute>Vale.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1714-12-19">19. <abbr>Dec.</abbr> 1714</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>